1. *Otrov* je veoma opasan za ljudsko zdravlje. (The poison is very dangerous for human health.)

2. Ona je napravila napitak od *otrova*. (She made a potion out of poison.)

3. On je ušao u prostoriju punu *otrova*. (He entered a room full of poison.)

4. Oni su za svoje zločine koristili *otrov*. (They used poison for their crimes.)

5. Ona je nesvesno uzela *otrov*. (She accidentally took the poison.)

6. Posle njegove smrti, utvrđeno je da je u pitanju bio *otrov*. (After his death, it was determined that it was a poison.)